snippet.title: MonsterKook
snippet.description:
Welcome to 'MonsterKook' Channel.
I like to make all sorts of stuff, with all sorts of materials. I have lots of projects including Cardboard, woodworking, electronics, prop making and more!

These videos are my attempts to teach and inspire others to make what they want to have. Let's hope you can see something here that will inspire you to create something with passion!
